Affiliate Functionality Testing - OpenCart Demo
Overview
This Readme provides details for evaluating the Affiliate functionality on the OpenCart demo e-commerce website (AUT). 
The primary objectives are to assess the functionality, performance, and usability of the affiliate feature.

Demo Website
OpenCart Demo

Objectives
Functional Testing: Ensure that the affiliate feature operates as expected.
Usability Testing: Evaluate the user experience related to the affiliate feature.

Testing Tasks
1. Functional Testing
Homepage Links:
Verify that all links on the homepage navigate to the correct pages.
Affiliate Feature:
Test the affiliate functionality with different keywords and verify that the results are accurate.
Check if the affiliate feature displays information correctly.
Add affiliate information and verify that it is correctly processed and displayed.
2. Usability Testing
Navigation:
Evaluate the ease of navigation through the affiliate sections of the website.
Product Information:
Assess the clarity and accessibility of product information within the affiliate context.
User Experience:
Provide feedback on the overall user experience related to the affiliate functionality, including ease of use and accessibility.
Test Cases
Functional Testing
Homepage Links:

Test Case 1: Click on each link on the homepage and verify the destination page.
Expected Result: All links should direct to the correct pages without errors.
Affiliate Feature:

Test Case 2: Search using various keywords within the affiliate feature and verify search results.
Expected Result: Search results should be accurate and relevant.

Test Case 3: Add new affiliate information and check if it displays correctly.
Expected Result: Added information should appear as expected and be correctly formatted.
Usability Testing
Navigation:

Test Case 4: Navigate through the affiliate sections and report on ease of navigation.
Expected Result: Navigation should be intuitive and straightforward.
Product Information:

Test Case 5: Assess the readability and accessibility of product details related to the affiliate section.
Expected Result: Product information should be clear and easily accessible.
User Experience:

Test Case 6: Provide feedback on the overall user experience with the affiliate feature.
Expected Result: The user experience should be satisfactory, with any issues or suggestions noted.

Feedback
Please document any issues or observations during testing and provide detailed feedback on both functionality and usability.
